            StyleBox["\<\"FindPfaffianSystem[HypSeries, SumVar, Vars] derives \
the Pfaffian system associated with HypSeries, automatically constructing a \
basis of derivatives from the holonomic order of the system.\\nHypSeries is a \
hypergeometric series given in terms of Pochhammer functions.\\nSumVar is the \
list of summation indices appearing in HypSeries:\\n  \[Bullet] {m, n, \
...}\\nVars is the list of kinematic variables:\\n  \[Bullet] {x, y, \
...}\\nThe result is the 4-tuple {HypSeries, SumVar, Pfaffian, Basis}, where \
Pfaffian is the Association <|Var \[Rule] Matrix|> of connection matrices and \
Basis is the list of basis elements. The 4-tuple is the input format expected \
by TransportDE[].\\nExamples:\\n  FindPfaffianSystem[Pochhammer[a,m+n] \
Pochhammer[b,m] Pochhammer[b',n] / (Pochhammer[c,m+n] m! n!) x^m y^n, {m, n}, \
{x, y}]\"\>", "InformationUsageText",
             StripOnInput->False,
